{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "A chatbot service, designated for the Covenant University Doctor (CUDoctor) telehealth system, has been crafted employing fuzzy logic rules and fuzzy inference presented by Omoregbe et al., 2020 41.",
    "This specialized service is designed to evaluate symptoms associated with tropical diseases prevalent in Nigeria.",
    "The Telegram Bot Application Programming Interface (API) establishes the connection between the chatbot and the system, while the Twilio API facilitates connectivity between the system and Short Messaging Service (SMS) subscribers.",
    "The service draws upon a knowledge base enriched with established facts about diseases and symptoms derived from medical ontologies.",
    "To predict diseases effectively based on inputted symptoms, a fuzzy support vector machine (SVM) is employed."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "A chatbot service, designated for the Covenant University Doctor (CUDoctor) telehealth system, has been crafted employing fuzzy logic rules and fuzzy inference presented by Omoregbe et al., 2020 41."
  ]
}